steps.name: I check that the "Account Screen" is displayed
I check that the "Wallet Screen" is displayed
I wait for the "CREDIT CARD" list to have more or equal than 1 elements
I check the number of "CREDIT CARDS" added
I check that the actual value: "3" is greater or equal than value "1"
I click on 1st/nd/rd/th "CREDIT CARD THREE DOTS" button
I check that the "Remove Payment Card Pane" is displayed
I click on "YES, DELETE MY CARD" button
I check that the "Card successfully removed" toast message is displayed
I wait for the "CREDIT CARD" list to have more or equal than 2 elements
I check the number of "CREDIT CARDS" added
I check that the actual value: "2" is less than value "3"
